Dear Respawn Entertainment(EA),


dont get me wrong on this one. Making steady content updates and providing the game with lore the way you do it is fantastic and people like it. But it just wont matter. Game servers are trash since season one. There was not one evening in the last week where i could play the game due to lobby issues and laggy servers. And i live in the capitol of germany. There is a cheater in nearly every ranked game i play.The technical side of your game is rotten. Really good players start to leave the game know even thought they love the gameplay. The last ALGS stream i watched was at such a low quality that i just turned it off besides the fact that i want to play there myself and i enjoy watching my favorite game in esports. PLAYERS NOW GET THE FEELING THAT YOU HAVE THE INTENTION TO LET YOUR GAME DIE. More content will not help with this issues QQ.

snippet.textDisplay:
My theory on Bloodhound’s past so we can get over this stupid gender debate

Bloodhound was born female. During the event of the cinematic, she takes up the title of Bloodhound and “becomes” Bloodhound. All that matters to them is the hunt and praising the Allfather.

In short, the person in the suit has a gender, but Bloodhound has no gender.
